dct_title_s: Map of Ridgefield Park, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from North Avenue to the Bergen Turnpike along Hacksensack River. Map displays the road names and layout of Ridgefield Park. Overpeck Creek and the Trolly to Hackensack are also depicted.
